channel.title: Need testers for something im making
channel.description:
Hi guys, for the last few days I have been making a forum system, and a server status system, I need a few testers, to find any glitches with it. After I get home from school today, I will intergrate them so that you need to log in to use the status checker.... All testers that join today will get free mod. link: www.runescape3.uk.to/login/register.php <-- to register to forums www.runescape3.uk.to/status/index.php <--for the status checker
PS: can you also rate from 1-10, and these are my first projects, so please be easy.
